Package: mimocode
Version: 0.1.6
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, clang, glibc, tar
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/XiaomiMiMo/MiMo-Code
Description: AI‑powered coding assistant (glibc wrapper for Termux)
 MiMo‑Code is an intelligent code completion and generation tool.
 This package downloads the official Linux ARM64 or x86_64 binary
 and runs it inside the Termux glibc environment.
